{"tid":1841270,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人入黎投票 支持醫護罷工要求政府封關","createTime":"2020-01-25T08:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:23:56.000Z","uid":265535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e246d0278da055c438eb0e403bf84e8f6dc493","tid":1841270,"uid":265535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"醫護需要你地支持！！！<br />\n支唔支持醫護罷工？<br />\n投票連結:<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FTopic.php%3Fid%3D1008&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=b1b982a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008</a> <br />\n投票時限:一個月，至 2 月 23 日止<br />\n<br />\n一眾熱心的市民已於 2020 年 1 月 24 日凌晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起 了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容 如下:<br />\n<br />\n截至 2020 年 1 月 25 日凌晨為止，24 小時內已有 1117 名香港市民投票，當中約 97%支持香 港醫護人員罷工，約 2%反對及 2 張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供 民意基礎。《香港地投票》已去信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎 病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時 24 小時內投票結果:<br />\n由 2020 年 1 月 24 日凌晨至 2020 年 1 月 25 日凌晨 受訪市民:共 1117 人<br />\n支持市民有 1092 人，反對市民有 23 人，2 票廢票<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=abe59669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"653bf5a45dc8729ec2956781e6704de1617c0469","tid":1841270,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ee4fb9e9225220dafcd20a358e927213d714d1e","tid":1841270,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"乜撚野網嚟，乜都㩒唔到，投HA secret 個算"},{"pid":"4dda246ea4d60aa6f47c21fb3da4361976aa92f2","tid":1841270,"uid":118276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔係網黎 要download個app<br />\n呢個App五毛係投唔到 同每人只投到一票<br />\n公信力比secret page高好多"},{"pid":"7eabe7ceea6bfdd5408da80c1d537231537f3160","tid":1841270,"uid":118276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9z4qeRe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9z4qeRe.jpg&h=0b779ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"07092c36465f2878a9f31214f7c54b80eb7fca6b","tid":1841270,"uid":118276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee4fb9e9225220dafcd20a358e927213d714d1e","tid":1841270,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"乜撚野網嚟，乜都㩒唔到，投HA secret 個算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"兩邊都投好辛苦你咩？"},{"pid":"cfef72a125423be1a4c5f77f9bff4ed38a70b5d2","tid":1841270,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"一齊入去表達意見！！！"},{"pid":"baeb400d7f7bffbe1b86568b08020b8757ecfb2b","tid":1841270,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"f0b1582921232f189928486267af022d66f215ea","tid":1841270,"uid":2587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"push 唔可以再咁自私淨係係網上表態支持醫護喇，根本係自hi同埋唔會比政府當一回事。要同醫護同行，一定要一齊罷工。先可以比到壓力政府去落實封關。"},{"pid":"18bc92045bd6d834c236682224165d7ea4f4582f","tid":1841270,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b1582921232f189928486267af022d66f215ea","tid":1841270,"uid":2587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"push 唔可以再咁自私淨係係網上表態支持醫護喇，根本係自hi同埋唔會比政府當一回事。要同醫護同行，一定要一齊罷工。先可以比到壓力政府去落實封關。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"649ec2d599539fc00fcf85b209708f13f427c89a","tid":1841270,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b1582921232f189928486267af022d66f215ea","tid":